name: GotM October 2021 - Curve Dasher DX
description:
First edition of "Game of the Month". I will be releasing one game each month under this line for the rest of 2021 and into 2022. Future games will release on other platforms alongside HEN.

Curve Dasher DX is an arcade snake-like in which you dash into pellets to earn points. But be careful, if you aren't dashing, pellets can result in a game over!

Arrow Keys - Steer / Menu Select
Z / C - Dash / Select
